The paper deals with event detection in videos using distributional semantic embeddings, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper also involves multimedia processing (cs.MM), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques.
